    {
      "@type": "del:Contribution",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_message_de568861-45fd-4aaf-a79c-893a3ca7ca7e",
      "del:text": "I picked <CARD> and <CARD>",
      "del:madeBy": {
        "@id": "participant_2"
      },
      "del:hasTopic": {
        "@id": "delidata_topic_1f798e00-5575-45b5-ae30-a98964b2a609"
      },
      "del:hasArgument": {
        "@id": "delidata_argument_de568861-45fd-4aaf-a79c-893a3ca7ca7e"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Contribution",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_message_e59d5e32-ab26-4330-88dc-7a40e28ca4b0",
      "del:text": "'The rule is \" All cards with vowels on one side have an even number on the other \" ; we could check <CARD> but it wouldn''t tell us anything , because the rule doesn''t say what needs to be on the opposite side of even numbers ; just on the opposite side of Vowels .'",
      "del:madeBy": {
        "@id": "participant_1"
      },
      "del:hasTopic": {
        "@id": "delidata_topic_1f798e00-5575-45b5-ae30-a98964b2a609"
      },
      "del:hasArgument": {
        "@id": "delidata_argument_e59d5e32-ab26-4330-88dc-7a40e28ca4b0"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Contribution",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_message_8c4f378e-99d5-4912-8b77-5f11f9b0990b",
      "del:text": "'So if the opposite side of <CARD> was , say , a B , that wouldn''t say the rule is wrong . Because the rule just says IF there''s a vowel , THEN must have an even number on the back .'",
      "del:madeBy": {
        "@id": "participant_1"
      },
      "del:hasTopic": {
        "@id": "delidata_topic_1f798e00-5575-45b5-ae30-a98964b2a609"
      },
      "del:hasArgument": {
        "@id": "delidata_argument_8c4f378e-99d5-4912-8b77-5f11f9b0990b"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Contribution",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_message_cff0cabe-cd02-4ee7-ac51-d996eddc401a",
      "del:text": "Not that there must also be vowels behind every even number .",
      "del:madeBy": {
        "@id": "participant_1"
      },
      "del:hasTopic": {
        "@id": "delidata_topic_1f798e00-5575-45b5-ae30-a98964b2a609"
      },
      "del:hasArgument": {
        "@id": "delidata_argument_cff0cabe-cd02-4ee7-ac51-d996eddc401a"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "del:Contribution",
      "del:identifier": "delidata_message_62fe05da-6a9f-4a55-9341-2384e77510f6",
      "del:text": "<CARD> should have a vowel on the back .",
      "del:madeBy": {
        "@id": "participant_3"
      },
      "del:hasTopic": {
        "@id": "delidata_topic_1f798e00-5575-45b5-ae30-a98964b2a609"
      },
      "del:hasArgument": {
        "@id": "delidata_argument_62fe05da-6a9f-4a55-9341-2384e77510f6"
